    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine sanctae et individuae Trinitatis. <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/79">Hugo</persName> et <persName key="#Emperor/king"
                            ref="#people/72">Lotharius</persName> divina favente clementia <rs
                            key="#Emperor/king">reges</rs>. Si sanctis ac venerabilibus locis ea
                        quae ab antecessoribus nostris collata sunt corroborare studuerimus, et de
                        his quae nostri iuris sunt concedere satagimus, aeternae vitae emolumentum
                        adipisci ac presentis status soliditatem propensius augmentari non
                        titubamus. Idcirco omnium fidelium sanctae Dei Ecclesiae nostrorumque
                        presentium ac futurorum industria noverit, <rs key="#Abbots">abbatem</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Monks">monachos</rs> in <rs key="#Monasteries">coenobio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Decima #Public_exactions #Angaria #Churches #Monasteries #Cells/hermitages #Abbots #Monks #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/301">domini et salvatoris nostri Iesu
                            Christi</orgName> militantes in <placeName
                            key="#Houses #Curtes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Landed_possessions #Decima #Public_exactions #Angaria #Churches #Monasteries #Cells/hermitages #Abbots #Monks #Royal_slave"
                            ref="#places/737">monte Amiate</placeName> nobis lacrimabiliter
                        protulisse, quod famis ac nuditatis indigentia ibidem Deo servire non
                        possent, eo quod <rs key="#Curtes">cortes</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Cells/hermitages">cellae</rs>, quae a predecessoribus nostris ad
                        sumptum eorum collatae sunt, a pravis fu[i]ssent distractae hominibus. Nos
                        quidem pro Dei amore animarumque nostrarum remedio, quoniam idem cenobium in
                        nostram devenerat potestatem ac proprietatem, res et predia, quae a nostris
                        precessoribus collata sunt et confirmata ac corroborata, confirmare et
                        corroborare studuimus, et <rs key="#Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure">de nostri
                            iuris proprietate in monachorum sumptum</rs> cortes et cellas
                        contulimus, quatenus sedulo orationes pro nobis matreque nostra <persName
                            key="#parentOf" ref="#people/1524">Berta</persName> ibidem ad Dominum
                        dirigantur. Igitur cortes et cellas, <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >massaricia</rs> et <rs key="#Landed_possessions">sortes</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Royal_slave">familiamque utriusque sexus</rs> quae hactenus
                        tenuerunt, omniaque precepta ab antecessoribus nostris conlata, omniaque
                        instrumenta confirmamus pleniterque corroboramus; et quoniam prefatum
                        cenobium in nostram devenit potestatem et proprietatem, ex quae a pravis
                        ablata sunt hominibus et alia quibus indigentiam explere valeant, in usum
                        fratrum per hoc nostrum preceptum concedimus, donamus atque largimur,
                        videlicet <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1512"><rs key="#Cells/hermitages">cellam</rs>
                            <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#places/1949">Sacti Benedicti</placeName></orgName>, <rs
                            key="#Curtes">curtem</rs> de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/334"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/764">Palea</placeName></geogName>, cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/303">Sancti Stephani in <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#places/757">[Monti]clo</placeName></orgName>, et cellam
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/302">Sanctae Mariae in <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#places/756">Lamulas</placeName></orgName>, corticellam de
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/331"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/760">Mustia</placeName></geogName>, [nec]non et
                        corticellam de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/335"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1951">Titinano</placeName></geogName>, et in <placeName
                            ref="#places/1952"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Coloni/tenants #Angaria"
                            >Cerri</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Coloni/tenants #Angaria">angariales</rs>, et <rs key="#Curtes"
                            >curticellam</rs> in <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/761"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/2315">Fereniano</geogName></placeName>, nec non et
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/308">cellam Sancti Salvatoris</orgName> in
                            <placeName ref="#places/762"
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >vale Racana</placeName>, et curticellam de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/332">Cuniclo</geogName> cum ipso caiolo de <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/1953">Porciano</placeName>, et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1455">Sancti Stephani</orgName> in <placeName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#places/430">Terquino</placeName>, seu et cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1513"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1950">Sancti Severi</placeName></orgName> super <rs
                            key="#Lakes">lacum</rs> cum ipsa corticella de <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/333"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1956">Besantio</placeName></geogName>, cellam etiam
                            <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1514"><placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#places/1955">Sancti Miniati</placeName></orgName>, nec non et
                        cellam <orgName
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1515">Sanctae Mariae de <placeName
                                key="#Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Cells/hermitages"
                                ref="#places/2734">Valeriano</placeName></orgName> cum ipsis rebus
                        de <placeName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#places/1964"><geogName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#estates/2346">Curticiole</geogName></placeName>, cum omnibus
                        adiacentiis et pertinentiis earum, atque cortem <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2309"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1969">Sanctae Mariae ad Offena</placeName></geogName>,
                        et curticellam <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2310"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1968">Sancti Simeonis</placeName></geogName> et
                            <geogName
                            key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            ref="#estates/2311"><placeName
                                key="#Curtes #Fiscal_property #Textual_occurrence #Object #Function #Exceptive #Fiscal_reserve #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ref="#places/1970">Sanctum Petrum in
                        Cervaria</placeName></geogName>, cum omnibus rebus et familiis ad eas in
                        integrum pertinentibus vel respicientibus. Denique etiam concedimus predicto
                        cenobio omnia <rs key="#Decima">decima</rs>, <rs key="#Public_exactions"
                            >frea</rs> et <rs key="#Profits_of_justice">iudiciaria</rs> et omnem
                        compositionem et exibitionem publicam ex omnibus <rs key="#Manentes"
                            >manentibus</rs> predicti monasterii ob remedium animarum nostrarum
                        matrisque nostrae in usum peregrinorum ad portam monasterii clamantium,
                        precipimus etiam et statuimus, ut deinceps in futurum haec nostra
                        confirmatio atque donatio a posteris nostris inconvulsa maneat et inlibata,
                        et ut nullus dux, marchio, comes, vicecomes aut ulla regni nostri magna
                        parvaque persona in domos vel res predicti cenobii violentiam inferat aut
                        famulos flagellare vel angariare presumat, neque de predictis rebus ullam
                        minorationem facere satagat; sed liceat abbatem sanctamque congregationem
                        predictas cortes et cellas cum eorum integritatibus tenere, omnium
                        inquie[tudi]ne remota. Si quis igitur hoc nostrum preceptum v√¨olare
                        temptaverit, sciat se compositurum <rs key="#Penalty">auri optimi libras
                            centum</rs>, <rs key="#Camera_regis">medietatem kamerae nostrae</rs> et
                            <rs key="#Camera_of_other_public_authorities">medietatem sanctae
                            congregationi predicti cenobii</rs>. Quod ut veius credatur
                        diligentiusque observetur, manibus propriis roborantes anuli nostri
                        inpressione subter iussimus insigniri. Signa serenissimorum (MF) (MF) domni
                        Hugonis et Lotharii regum. <persName key="#Chaplain" ref="#people/1535"
                            >Giseprandus</persName> domnorum regum <rs key="#Chaplain"
                            >capellanus</rs> regi iussu recognovi et subscripsi. Data III non.
                        octub., anno dominicae incarnationis DCCCCXXXVII, regni vero domni Hugonis
                        regis XII, filii [ve]ro eius Lotharii item regis VII, indictione XI. Actum
                        ad <placeName ref="#places/1971">pontem Andria</placeName>. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
